abi: event AccountCreated(address[] owners, uint256 indexed ids, uint256 timestamp)
event Deposit(address indexed user, uint256 indexed accountId, uint256 amount, uint256 timestamp)
event WithdrawalRequested(address indexed user, uint256 indexed accountId, uint256 withdrawalId, uint256 amount, uint256 timestamp)
function getApprovals(uint256 accountId, uint256 withdrawId) view returns (uint256)
